<i>Of course you</i>                   
<i>didn't say that.</i>                


716
00:49:57,428 --> 00:49:59,895
So righteous.                   


717
00:49:59,930 --> 00:50:01,397
<i>Let me tell</i>                     
<i>you something.</i>                  


718
00:50:01,432 --> 00:50:05,134
<i>You're fake,</i>                    
<i>and just like me.</i>               


719
00:50:05,169 --> 00:50:06,668
<i>Everybody cheats.</i>               


720
00:50:08,639 --> 00:50:10,139
<i>Everybody steals.</i>               


721
00:50:10,508 --> 00:50:14,010
