          <i> Let him go!</i>          


761
00:53:17,728 --> 00:53:19,195
           [choking]            


762
00:53:19,230 --> 00:53:20,796
      <i> (female)</i>                 
      <i> You're killing him!</i>      


763
00:53:20,831 --> 00:53:23,399
            Stop it!            


764
00:53:23,434 --> 00:53:24,933
             <i> Stop!</i>             


