770
00:53:47,124 --> 00:53:48,924
       Stop it! You're          
       hurting my mommy!        


771
00:53:49,694 --> 00:53:51,159
I'm sorry! I'm sorry.           


772
00:53:51,195 --> 00:53:53,862
     <i> (female)</i>                  
     <i> Dylan, baby,</i>              
     <i> get back to the car!</i>      


773
00:53:53,897 --> 00:53:56,565
I'm sorry.                      
I didn't know.                  


774
00:53:56,601 --> 00:53:58,334
