777
00:54:01,739 --> 00:54:03,839
       We don't need            
       your kind of help.       


778
00:54:06,544 --> 00:54:09,378
       Mommy, why               
       were you fighting?       


779
00:54:15,219 --> 00:54:17,219
<i>(female)</i>                        
<i>We don't need</i>                   
<i>your charity.</i>                   


780
00:54:17,255 --> 00:54:19,788
        <i> (Josh)</i>                 
        <i> It's not charity, okay?</i>


781
00:54:22,793 --> 00:54:26,462
         <i> It's payment for</i>      
         <i> teaching me something.</i>


782
00:54:28,633 --> 00:54:32,067
          I thought I'd changed,
