884
01:03:50,593 --> 01:03:52,093
          [screaming]           


885
01:03:52,362 --> 01:03:54,796
    <i> --there are men that</i>       
    <i> are trying to shoot us.</i>    


886
01:03:54,832 --> 01:03:56,298
    <i> We're at 43 Pitch Road.</i>    


887
01:03:56,333 --> 01:03:57,799
