896
01:04:35,906 --> 01:04:37,538
         Drop the gun.          


897
01:04:37,574 --> 01:04:39,074
             Do it!             


898
01:04:51,989 --> 01:04:54,222
You, get outta here!            


899
01:04:54,258 --> 01:04:55,924
           Do as she says, girl.


900
01:04:58,195 --> 01:04:59,660
Run!                            


901
01:04:59,696 --> 01:05:01,196
<i>Run!</i>                            


902
01:05:01,631 --> 01:05:03,564
Go now!                         


903
01:05:03,600 --> 01:05:06,701
      - Grandma, I can't.       
      - Go! Go now!             


904
01:05:08,372 --> 01:05:12,207
    [gunfire in background]     


905
01:05:13,911 --> 01:05:18,113
          <i> (Josh)</i>               
          <i> I shot 'em.</i>          


906
01:05:18,148 --> 01:05:20,415
       I killed 'em all.        


907
01:05:21,418 --> 01:05:24,719
       <i> And you know what?</i>      


908
01:05:24,754 --> 01:05:27,722
          It was easy.          


909
01:05:27,757 --> 01:05:29,257
        <i> I'm good at it.</i>        


910
01:05:30,227 --> 01:05:31,826
           [gunshots]           


911
01:05:31,861 --> 01:05:33,861
        [grunts in pain]        


912
01:05:36,233 --> 01:05:40,402
