913
01:05:44,174 --> 01:05:47,075
 <i> (Josh)</i>                        
 <i> It's the only thing</i>           
 <i> I've ever really been good at.</i>


914
01:05:52,049 --> 01:05:55,350
   I don't--                    
   I don't know what to say.    


